r information and recite at any moment  The main purpose of the Ratline is to assemble a class imbued with honor  discipline  pride  and respect conducted in phases of development  employing supporting virtues such as cohesion  humility  physical fitness  knowledge  and self reliance  First year cadets memorize the  Rat Bible  which contains information about the VMI system  the history of the Institute and the names of the cadets who were killed at the Battle of New Market  The rat experience begins with Matriculation Day  continues through winter and generally ends in January or February when rats  break out  It is a time of tough training  mentally and physically  to prepare you for the next three years in the Corps  Don t do ordinary  Because rats rely on one another during this time  it is in the Rat Line that the legendary Brother Rat bond is established Culture The VMI Experience Military Environment Honor System Citizen Soldier Athletics The First Year  Rat Year  The First Year   The Rat Line Throughout most of the first year  new cadets walk at rigid attention along a prescribed route inside barracks known as the  Rat Line   Cadets must be meticulous in keeping shoes shined  uniforms spotless  and in daily personal grooming  Additionally  new cadets must memorize school songs  yells  and other information and recite at any moment  The main purpose of the Ratline is to assemble a class imbued with honor  discipline  pride  and respect conducted in phases of development  employing supporting virtues such as cohesion  humility  physical fitness  knowledge  and self reliance  First year cadets memorize the  Rat Bible  which contains information about the VMI system  the history of the Institute and the names of the cadets who were killed at the Battle of New Market  The rat experience begins with Matriculation Day  continues through winter and generally ends in January or February when rats  break out  It is a time of tough training  mentally and physically  to